{"tid":1369714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727元朗] 當成最後一場遊行","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:55:10.000Z","uid":80972,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f846900bceb673c8fe5ff601d6cb72f8df0b5108","tid":1369714,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"身邊好多朋友<br />\n唔係住大西北都話入黎元朗<br />\n有d高矮肥瘦 都買齊裝<br />\n大家就算知道有潛在危險都入黎<br />\n聽日一定好多人一齊逼爆大馬路<br />\n<br />\n因為大家都想行出黎<br />\n話俾呢個垃圾政權聽<br />\n我地對721嘅憤怒   對反送中嘅堅持<br />\n對黑勢力嘅反抗<br />\n<br />\n大量公務員已經出黎表態<br />\n當中包括大量政府運作核心嘅 AO,EO<br />\n張建宗都出黎幫狗隊道歉，做埋白面<br />\n我相信佢已經準備好署任做特首<br />\n<br />\n一場完美嘅和理非遊行<br />\n就係對垃圾港共政府嘅致命一擊<br />\n<br />\n明天要點:<br />\n1. 互相照應，絕不落單<br />\n2. 不挑釁，不衝突，但必自衛<br />\n3. 要守，但不死守，日落前散水<br />\n<br />\n明天見!"},{"pid":"954e2fd09a984c11d6db03d06c59d8d6df448445","tid":1369714,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:36:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"cb9c9346f85091df9778103076fcfe9bca6f2bf9","tid":1369714,"uid":209050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3caa3d965cb1117884b188caf87a3c524af8e90b","tid":1369714,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"96edc9e83fd4ce28204d2f7149459b777d505105","tid":1369714,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"《突發行動》：727元朗尋犬，撚9日<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dqLxDT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dqLxDT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"91c7e5c19f17cc860c5ac67487196d2a5f5c847d","tid":1369714,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:36:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"d4a64d3971c7a2fdaa412bfd317f0ab2b243da8a","tid":1369714,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit